---

<section class="aurora-section" id="aurora">
  <!-- Photo background with parallax -->
  <div class="aurora-bg" id="aurora-bg">
    <img src="/images/aurora.webp" alt="Aurora Borealis" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
  </div>

  <div class="aurora-overlay"></div>

  <div class="aurora-content">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">
      <span class="eyebrow-num">003</span>
      <span class="eyebrow-line"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow-text">Northern Europe</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title" aria-label="Aurora Borealis">
      <span class="line">AURORA</span>
      <span class="line aurora-accent">BOREALIS</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="section-body">
      At 2am in a frozen field, the sky collapsed into light.
      <em> Curtains of green plasma</em> swept the horizon —
      charged particles colliding with the upper atmosphere,
      making the invisible visible for a few breathless hours.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

